org.apache.coyote.ajp

类 SimpleAjpClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.coyote.ajp.SimpleAjpClient

  • public class SimpleAjpClient
extends java.lang.Object
    AJP client that is not (yet) a full AJP client implementation as it just provides the functionality required for the unit tests. The client uses blocking IO throughout.
